{"tid":2459244,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點煮D肉先會唔「鞋」","createTime":"2021-03-24T04:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T06:52:46.000Z","uid":106042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b7fd97022522ad7fe91bd49c1f7653e4da4786","tid":2459244,"uid":106042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"除左用咩鬆肉粉 木瓜 菠蘿之外<br />\n<br />\n豬肉就一定煮熟先食<br />\n煎豬排如果唔落以上<br />\n好似多數都鞋<br />\n<br />\n煲湯豬肉<br />\n煲完多數又係鞋到食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近煮牛尾<br />\n煮左好耐都好「Un」<br />\n但放左雪櫃第二日翻熱就夠淋 <br />\n仲好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa36495d3ffdb35913d391189baf3ee5951a57","tid":2459244,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"用酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e483aa79280491bb51947b78f540d1376afc1ab1","tid":2459244,"uid":92401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"生食 唔好煮"},{"pid":"db3b08bad5e9cbae6ff0f20d53a95c558745f1d2","tid":2459244,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"慢煮棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529b01fd93ebf197f95b435eeed3c288bbfed1e6","tid":2459244,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3b08bad5e9cbae6ff0f20d53a95c558745f1d2","tid":2459244,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"慢煮棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"+1 神器"},{"pid":"f95c97afbf647fc8ed1bc0a7ffcb34325591fcc1","tid":2459244,"uid":322648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"你用咩位呀？用瘦肉點煮都鞋，豬扒可以試下用刀背/槌拍鬆佢"},{"pid":"